TO THE FIRM RIGHT NOW!

10:37.740 --> 10:38.900
WE HAVE THE TECHNOLOGY
TO DEAL WITH THIS, JULIA!

10:38.940 --> 10:40.908
- ADAM! ADAM!
- COME ON!
YOU'RE HAVING A BURGER. COME ON.

10:40.950 --> 10:42.451
