11:43.840 --> 11:45.558
- OH, IT WAS DELICIOUS.
- GOOD.

11:45.600 --> 11:47.522
- YEAH. I'M OUT OF HERE.
- OKAY, GOOD.

11:47.560 --> 11:48.549
- I'M GONNA GO.
- I'M SORRY.

11:48.600 --> 11:49.828
NO, I GET IT.
I GET IT.

11:49.880 --> 11:51.427
