TO BECOME ANY MORE AWKWARD

11:51.460 --> 11:53.189
BY REFUSING
YOUR BROTHER'S BURGER.

11:53.220 --> 11:54.869
- WHO ARE YOU?
- HI.

11:54.920 --> 11:59.539
SYD, UM, THERE ARE NICER WAYS
