12:09.450 --> 12:10.781
- OKAY.
- OKAY? LET'S GO.

12:10.830 --> 12:11.854
ALL RIGHT. I'M GONNA GO.
I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

12:11.900 --> 12:13.447
- IS THAT THE GUY?
- THAT'S THE GUY. THAT'S CHRIS.

12:13.490 --> 12:14.650
- NO, WE GOT TO GO.
- NO, YOU'RE PLAYING BALL.

12:14.690 --> 12:15.930
COME ON. COME ON,
GUYS, LET'S GO.

12:15.970 --> 12:17.653
UH, GUYS, YOU DON'T WANT ME--
YOU DON'T WANT ME PLAYING BALL.

12:17.700 --> 12:19.622
HEY, TELL YOU WHAT.
YOU CAN BE TEAM CAPTAIN.

12:19.660 --> 12:21.048
BRING THE BALL. LET'S GO.

12:21.080 --> 12:23.287
- ALL RIGHT, COME ON.
- WE'RE GONNA
GO PLAY BASKETBALL.

12:23.320 --> 12:24.252
I'M GONNA MAKE THIS FAST.

12:24.290 --> 12:25.564
OKAY.

12:25.600 --> 12:27.397
[overlapping chatter]

12:27.430 --> 12:29.705
NO ULTERIOR MOTIVES

12:29.740 --> 12:33.915
ALL MY FOCUS ON YOU

12:34.820 --> 12:35.775
WELL, I CAN'T HIDE

12:35.820 --> 12:38.789
WHY THE LONG FACE?

12:38.820 --> 12:40.959
