12:41.000 --> 12:44.925
MY, UH--MY WIFE
PUT MY MOTORCYCLE IN JAIL.

12:44.970 --> 12:46.301
IT'S LOCKED UP.

12:46.350 --> 12:49.729
- OH, MAN.
- YEAH.

12:49.760 --> 12:52.763
WELL, I CAN SEE THAT
BET AND RAISE YOU,

12:52.800 --> 12:56.975
BECAUSE I GOT NO WHEELS AT ALL,
TWO OR FOUR.

12:57.010 --> 12:59.183
