AS A CHAUFFEUR.

12:59.220 --> 13:00.903
OOF. OOF.

13:00.950 --> 13:05.569
THEN SHE'S GONNA TAKE ME
TO PHYSICAL THERAPY ON MONDAY.

13:05.610 --> 13:07.840
SO, I MEAN, UH,
IT'S GONNA TAKE ABOUT A WEEK.

13:07.890 --> 13:11.712
[chuckles]
MM. MONDAY?

13:11.750 --> 13:13.638
- YEAH.
- I'LL DRIVE YOU.

13:13.680 --> 13:14.886
YEAH, YEAH, LET ME DRIVE YOU.

13:14.930 --> 13:16.545
- REALLY?
- YEAH, YEAH.

13:16.580 --> 13:17.751
WE'LL MAKE A DAY OF IT.

13:17.790 --> 13:19.849
SO WE'LL GET THE WOMEN
OUT OF THE PICTURE.

13:19.900 --> 13:21.037
WE'LL GO TOGETHER.
IT'LL BE GREAT.

13:21.070 --> 13:22.799
I'M LOOKING FORWARD TO IT.OKAY.

13:22.830 --> 13:25.390
GIRL, WHO'S KIDDING

13:25.420 --> 13:27.172
PUT IT UP! PUT IT UP!

13:27.220 --> 13:28.073
- OH!
- OH!

13:28.110 --> 13:30.351
I'LL BE BACK.
I'M GONNA GO LAY HER DOWN.

13:30.390 --> 13:32.802
OKAY. NAP TIME.

13:32.840 --> 13:34.182
YOU KEEP SURPRISING ME

13:34.220 --> 13:36.780
WITH ALL YOUR THOUGHTS
AND VIEWS

13:36.810 --> 13:41.258
NA NA NA NA NA NA NA NA

13:41.300 --> 13:43.268
OH!

13:46.200 --> 13:48.430
- OH, YOU GOT TO TAKE IT OUT!
- OH!

13:48.480 --> 13:49.617
PUT IT UP!

13:49.650 --> 13:53.234
OH, NICE!
[clapping]

13:53.280 --> 13:55.475
OH!

13:55.520 --> 13:56.748
PUT IT UP!

13:56.800 --> 13:59.894
- YEAH!
- OH!

13:59.940 --> 14:02.101
- ALL RIGHT. BE READY, SYD. - GET IT, SYD! OH!

