14:17.160 --> 14:20.812
YEAH, THESE MINIATURE VANS
HAVE FULL-SIZED POWER NOWADAYS.

14:20.860 --> 14:22.714
IN FACT,
I'M GONNA UP THE EXPERIENCE.

14:22.750 --> 14:24.092
- AH.
- YEAH.

14:24.130 --> 14:26.018
A LITTLE WIND IN THE HAIR, HUH?

14:26.070 --> 14:26.923
- THERE YOU GO!
- EASY RIDERSTYLE.

14:26.960 --> 14:27.995
- THERE YOU GO.
- GET THESE BUFFOONS

14:28.030 --> 14:30.169
