ON THE RIGHT-HAND SIDE.

14:30.210 --> 14:32.587
THIS IS US? RIGHT HERE.
OH. I GOT IT. I'M ON IT.

14:32.630 --> 14:34.518
- HOLD ON. HOLD ON!
- COMING IN HOT.
COMING IN HOT.

14:34.560 --> 14:35.788
- OH.
- OKAY.

14:35.840 --> 14:37.649
- OH, MAN! OH, YEAH!
- YEAH.

14:37.700 --> 14:40.828
[tires screech]

14:40.880 --> 14:43.769
- OH, AND WE'RE EARLY.
- YEAH?

14:43.810 --> 14:44.799
I'M GONNA PARK.
I'LL COME IN WITH YOU.

14:44.840 --> 14:45.875
- WE'RE EARLY?
- YEAH.

14:45.910 --> 14:46.945
I HAD MY EYES CLOSED.

14:46.980 --> 14:48.982
I FEEL LIKE
I'VE GONE THROUGH TIME.

14:49.020 --> 14:50.669
- YOU'RE A DAY EARLY.
- OH, MAN.

14:50.710 --> 14:51.950
I'LL HANG IN THE WAITING ROOM
WITH YOU, IF THAT'S--

14:51.990 --> 14:53.298
NO, NO, NO. COME ON.
THAT'S SILLY.

14:53.340 --> 14:55.717
