- I DON'T THINK SO.
- YOU SURE?

15:05.520 --> 15:06.657
- YEAH, I'M SURE.
- OKAY.

15:06.690 --> 15:08.897
I DID SEE A VINTAGE GUITAR SHOP
AROUND THE CORNER, SO--

15:08.940 --> 15:10.316
OKAY.
ALL RIGHT.

15:10.350 --> 15:12.102
