15:22.640 --> 15:25.256
- HEY, MAX.
- HEY, BUD.

15:25.300 --> 15:28.508
WE JUST WANTED TO HAVE
A QUICK CONVERSATION WITH YOU

15:28.540 --> 15:30.599
ABOUT THIS GIRL THAT YOU LIKE.DYLAN.

15:30.650 --> 15:32.049
- YES, DYLAN.
- YEAH, DYLAN.

15:32.100 --> 15:33.374
WE JUST WANTED TO TALK TO YOU

15:33.410 --> 15:36.061
ABOUT HOW THESE RELATIONSHIPS
BETWEEN YOUNG BOYS

15:36.100 --> 15:37.408
AND GIRLS WORK.MM-HMM.

