BUT HERE'S THE THING.

15:41.590 --> 15:43.103
YOUR DAD AND I HAVE BEEN
IN A RELATIONSHIP

15:43.140 --> 15:46.177
FOR SO LONG THAT WE ARE
PRACTICALLY EXPERTS AT IT,

15:46.220 --> 15:48.359
AND WE'VE LEARNED A LOT
ALONG THE WAY,

15:48.390 --> 15:50.005
SO WE WANTED
TO SHARE OUR KNOWLEDGE WITH YOU.

15:50.050 --> 15:51.631
[Max]
NORMALLY TO BECOME
AN EXPERT IN SOMETHING,

15:51.670 --> 15:53.877
YOU HAVE TO NOT JUST
HAVE DONE IT FOR A LONG TIME

15:53.910 --> 15:55.150
BUT HAVE AN ADVANCED
DEGREE AS WELL.

15:55.190 --> 15:56.293
