ADVANCED DEGREES

15:56.330 --> 15:57.604
IN RELATIONSHIPS, MAX,
BUT IF THEY DID...

15:57.640 --> 15:58.743
- THEY SHOULD.
- WE'D HAVE IT.

15:58.780 --> 15:59.508
I CAN GUARANTEE THAT YOUR
MOTHER AND I WOULD HAVE ONE.

15:59.540 --> 16:00.848
- WE'D HAVE IT FOR SURE.
- YEAH.

16:00.890 --> 16:02.027
WHAT'S YOUR WISDOM?

16:02.060 --> 16:02.981
OKAY. WHERE DO YOU
WANT TO START?
GREAT.

16:03.030 --> 16:06.477
UM, WELL, WHAT WE'VE LEARNED
ALONG THE WAY

16:06.510 --> 16:08.375
IS THAT SOMETIMES
IN RELATIONSHIPS,

16:08.410 --> 16:10.890
PEOPLE CAN LIKE EACH OTHER
AT DIFFERENT LEVELS.

16:10.930 --> 16:11.919
- RIGHT?
- RIGHT.

16:11.970 --> 16:13.130
_ 50--
- SO, FOR EXAMPLE,

16:13.170 --> 16:15.138
ON A SCALE OF ONE TO FIVE,
FIVE BEING HIGHEST,

16:15.180 --> 16:16.932
YOU MIGHT LIKE SOMEBODY
AT A FIVE, AND THEY MIGHT

16:16.970 --> 16:18.198
LIKE YOU BACK ONLY AT A TWO...

16:18.250 --> 16:20.309
- RIGHT.
