WANT TO BE YOUR FRIEND.

16:20.350 --> 16:22.489
THAT'S NORMAL.
IT'S A VERY NORMAL THING.

16:22.530 --> 16:23.485
WHAT ARE YOUR NUMBERS?

16:23.530 --> 16:24.974
FOR EACH OTHER?

16:25.010 --> 16:26.568
WELL, WE'RE BOTH AT A FIVE.FIVE.

16:26.600 --> 16:28.181
- RIGHT?
- YUP.

16:28.220 --> 16:30.017
AND THAT IS USUALLY HOW
ROMANTIC RELATIONSHIPS WORK.

16:30.050 --> 16:32.632
PEOPLE LIKE EACH OTHER
THE SAME AMOUNT.

16:32.680 --> 16:33.874
- MM-HMM.
- ROBUST FIVE.

16:33.920 --> 16:35.979
- IT HAS A BALANCE.
- YEAH.

16:36.020 --> 16:37.647
