UP TO A FIVE.

17:22.830 --> 17:23.797
SO YOU'RE STILL FRIENDS.

17:23.830 --> 17:25.752
YES.
WE'LL ALWAYS BE FRIENDS.

17:25.800 --> 17:29.247
[laughs]
GOOD FRIENDS.

17:29.280 --> 17:30.349
HUH.

17:30.390 --> 17:32.312
[dogs barking]
