OF THIS PUZZLE MISSING.

17:40.160 --> 17:41.081
OH, YOU NOTICED THAT?
YEAH.

17:41.120 --> 17:42.564
- YEAH.
- WELL, YEAH.

17:42.610 --> 17:44.578
YES.I KNOW I DON'T HAVE A DOG...

17:44.610 --> 17:45.816
