17:45.850 --> 17:48.262
BUT I GREW UP WITH A BROWN
LAB AND A BORDER COLLIE,

17:48.300 --> 17:51.235
AND I JUST MISS
HAVING THEM AROUND, SO--

17:51.270 --> 17:52.498
YOU KNOW, BUT I LIVE
IN A TINY APARTMENT NOW,

17:52.550 --> 17:56.611
AND I DECIDED THAT
I WOULD CROWDSOURCE MY NEEDS.

17:56.660 --> 17:57.729
[chuckles]

17:57.760 --> 18:00.240
