39:38.470 --> 39:41.098
- GREAT LOVER OF ANIMALS.
- MM-HMM.

39:41.130 --> 39:43.542
YOU'RE, UM, HONEST.

39:43.580 --> 39:45.957
YOU'RE VERY, VERY HONEST.

39:46.000 --> 39:48.969
YOU ARE BRAVE.

39:49.000 --> 39:50.934
YOU HAVE A HUGE HEART.

39:50.970 --> 39:53.382
HOW FAR

39:53.420 --> 39:57.902
CAN I GO?

39:57.940 --> 39:59.976
WHO ARE YOU?

40:00.010 --> 40:03.969
DO YOU EVEN HAVE A CLUE?
[door opens]

40:04.020 --> 40:06.636
- HEY.
- HI.

40:06.680 --> 40:09.080
YOU LOOK FANTASTIC.

40:09.130 --> 40:12.463
- THANK YOU.
- YEAH.

40:12.510 --> 40:14.398
SO I HOPE YOU'RE READY

40:14.440 --> 40:16.362
FOR SOME ABSOLUTELY AMAZING
FRENCH CUISINE

40:16.410 --> 40:18.025
BECAUSE I FOUND
THE PERFECT PLACE TO TAKE YOU.

40:18.070 --> 40:19.378
- OH? WHERE?
- MM-HMM.

40:19.410 --> 40:22.789
IS THERE SOMEONE ELSE

40:22.830 --> 40:26.516
- YOU GROCERY SHOPPED?
- THERE'S TWO MORE JUST LIKE IT.

40:30.010 --> 40:30.658
MM-HMM.

40:30.700 --> 40:31.837
DOES THIS MEAN YOU'RE COOKING?

40:31.870 --> 40:33.110
I'M COOKING.

40:33.150 --> 40:37.211
- YOU DON'T COOK.
- I DON'T GROCERY SHOP EITHER.

40:37.260 --> 40:40.149
OKAY.
[laughs]

40:40.190 --> 40:44.012
LOOK, I'M SORRY IF I'VE BEEN
PUTTING PRESSURE ON YOU

40:44.060 --> 40:45.391
TO DEFINE THINGS.

40:45.440 --> 40:49.092
I'M REALLY SORRY
THAT I CRASHED YOUR BARBECUE.

40:49.130 --> 40:51.997
I'M REALLY SORRY ABOUT THAT.

40:52.030 --> 40:55.966
I, UH--I LIKE THIS.

40:56.000 --> 40:57.854
I LIKE THIS,
AND I JUST WANT TO KEEP GOING

40:57.900 --> 41:01.063
AT WHATEVER SPEED
YOU'RE COMFORTABLE WITH.

41:03.460 --> 41:04.415
I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU'RE COOKING.

41:04.460 --> 41:07.623
NO ONE IS MORE
SURPRISED THAN I AM.

41:07.670 --> 41:11.117
I MAY HAVE OVERSOLD THE
CUISINE JUST A TOUCH.

41:11.150 --> 41:12.117
- MM-HMM.
- YEAH.

41:12.150 --> 41:13.253
BUT I CAN PROMISE YOU

41:13.290 --> 41:15.155
THERE'S NOT GONNA BE
ANY GOSSIPY MOMS IN MY KITCHEN.

41:15.190 --> 41:17.329
DO YOU KNOW YOUR FAMILY?

41:17.370 --> 41:19.326
YOU KNOW WHAT?
LET'S GO OUT.

41:19.370 --> 41:20.917
YEAH.OUT, LIKE IN PUBLIC?

41:20.960 --> 41:21.847
- OUT.
- REALLY?

41:21.890 --> 41:22.811
- LET'S GO OUT.
- YOU SURE ABOUT THIS?

41:22.850 --> 41:23.851
LET'S GO THE FRENCH PLACE.

41:23.890 --> 41:24.925
YOU WANT TO GO
TO THE FRENCH PLACE?

41:24.960 --> 41:25.949
YEAH.

41:26.000 --> 41:27.069
THERE COULD BE MOMS
AT THE FRENCH PLACE.

41:27.100 --> 41:27.919
THERE COULD BE
MOMS AT THE FRENCH PLACE.

41:27.960 --> 41:30.440
- CAN YOU HANDLE THAT?
- I'LL LIVE.

42:18.600 --> 42:19.908
[dog barks]
